items.badge_description: After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 5 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock 2.
From the playground to your check-in, tag is a universally good time. Now tag some more friends while sharing your beer adventures.

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 45 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 10!

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 40 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 9!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 85 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock 18.
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 345 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock 70.

Put down those cases of Ale Yeast because unlike the IPA, the IPL is brewed with Lager Yeast and a generous amount of hops. When you want a punch of hops with a lighter finish, reach for an India Pale Lager. That's 20 different beers with the style of Lager - IPL (India Pale Lager). Try 5 more or Level 5!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 30 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 7.

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 195 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 40! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

So, you're new around here? Congrats on your first brew! This one's for you.

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 50 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 11!
